Because here there is more work. And

34:26.259 --> 34:42.921
you can find... ...merchandise or food, whatever 
it is... ...a little cheaper than in Mexico.

34:42.981 --> 34:43.281
Yes. Although right now everything is a little 
expensive here. Yes, right now it's bad.

34:48.628 --> 34:49.790
Everything is expensive now. Right now it's 
expensive too. Yes. Well... The war in Mexico, the

34:54.117 --> 34:56.220
revolution. Do you know any stories about this?

