About the revolution in Mexico? Yes, in Mexico. 
About

35:07.556 --> 35:10.901
what? About the men who were in the revolution or 
what?

35:18.272 --> 35:18.632
Well, yes. No, well, I don't know. I heard about it. 
There comes Pancho Villa, Obregon, I

35:23.581 --> 35:34.275
don't remember. And

35:34.295 --> 35:47.391
this is a thing from your experience, but it's a 
very old thing. Yes, many years ago. Well, some

35:50.024 --> 36:03.783
people say that the revolution was a good thing for 
Mexico, and others say that it was a bad

35:50.024 --> 36:03.783
thing. What do you think about this? Well, because 
I've heard of talks, now that I'm older, that there

36:09.490 --> 36:18.883
were some who were in the revolution, fighting

36:20.129 --> 36:30.959
for the good of Mexico, for all the people. They 
weren't fighting like others, like the others,

36:32.720 --> 36:47.554
because it was the government that was fighting 
and others who stood up against the government to

36:32.720 --> 36:47.554
fight. And there were some who talk now that they 
were fighting so that the

36:49.745 --> 37:03.101
poor people had something to eat. They stood up 
against it.

