Because of how poor there are many people. Well, in 
Mexico, before the revolution, there were many

37:13.690 --> 37:18.808
schools. For example, do you study in Mexico? Very 
little. Very little. Yes, because my mom came here

37:25.537 --> 37:31.623
and we have to work to maintain the trip. Yes. I like 
how she maintained us when we were little. Yes. How

37:38.471 --> 37:40.853
many years did you study? What? A little, but a 
little is a year or two years in school? About two

37:46.659 --> 37:47.841
years, three. Three? Yes. Did you read in Spanish? 
A little. Yes, and write too. A little bit too. And

37:55.742 --> 38:00.669
in English?

38:00.749 --> 38:07.077
I'm going to tell you the truth. I haven't learned 
English here with these people. They

38:12.144 --> 38:16.370
speak Spanish. They speak Spanish to me all the 
time. Yes. That's why I don't... I didn't learn to

38:22.270 --> 38:26.854
speak well with them. I understand what they say 
and all that. Yes. And it wasn't necessary to learn

38:29.577 --> 38:35.022
English. Well, yes, but it's very hard for me to 
speak English. Yes. A lady. Because if I say

38:46.193 --> 38:50.978
something that is not right, there it is. It's very 
different to talk to a lady than to talk to a

38:53.033 --> 38:57.139
gentleman. Yes.

39:01.545 --> 39:04.308
Is that true? Why? Well, because you can say 
something bad when you're talking to a lady who

39:05.590 --> 39:12.900
doesn't know English perfectly.

39:15.403 --> 39:18.528
But you speak a little bit of English. Well, a 
little bit of one thing, a little bit of another.

39:23.324 --> 39:23.804
Yes. Well, this old man doesn't speak English, he 
speaks Spanish. But I understand everything he

39:30.031 --> 39:34.295
tells me. He brings me things from there, he tells 
me in English, and I take it with me. This old man who

39:40.281 --> 39:45.486
works here with you, he doesn't speak Spanish? He 
speaks Spanish, but as I tell him. There are times

39:51.995 --> 40:03.207
that he says something to me in Spanish

39:51.995 --> 40:03.207
that is not true. But he is talking to me. And that's 
what I say. If I start speaking English with you, I

40:08.873 --> 40:13.358
can say something bad to you. And you don't think 
so. That's why it's very hard to talk to a woman.

40:25.603 --> 40:31.516
With a good man, it's much more different. Yes, 
it's easier with men. Yes, because if you say

40:33.801 --> 40:38.151
something bad, they don't pay much attention. 
Well, yes, maybe it's easier for men to talk to men

40:39.380 --> 40:48.131
and women. It's easier in many ways.

40:55.560 --> 40:56.381
Yes, ma'am. Well, your children speak English. 
