41:06.160 --> 41:09.766
correct English. Because he studied it a lot. And 
your daughters went to school, right? Yes, they

41:16.095 --> 41:21.063
went to school, but they don't speak the correct 
English like Antonio. You look at Antonio

41:22.024 --> 41:31.459
speaking English, and you say, well, he's an 
American who speaks English. Because he finished

41:33.970 --> 41:41.883
the whole school when he came from the service, 
from the army. Yes. He went to the school here in Del

41:42.324 --> 41:47.833
Mar to finish the school. Ah,

41:47.853 --> 41:51.219
yes. He went to the school to learn how to put 
stickers on the cars. Yes. He finished that

41:58.591 --> 41:59.573
school.

42:02.995 --> 42:11.485
And then he went to school to study mechanics at the 
distro. What do you call big engines? Diesel?

42:16.692 --> 42:17.913
Diesel, yes. He went to school for mechanics. Yes.

