42:59.375 --> 43:02.419
two. But at work I don't smoke anything. It doesn't 
tempt me to see other people who are smoking to make

43:06.964 --> 43:14.113
me want to smoke a cigarette. No. At home, yes. At 
night, when I just finished dinner, I turn on the

